Earth looked like a ball of nothingness.

01:02:30.559 --> 01:02:35.510
As He spoke it into existence,

01:02:35.520 --> 01:02:38.069
it was without form and void,

01:02:38.079 --> 01:02:39.829
and darkness was on the face of the

01:02:39.839 --> 01:02:42.549
deep. I could see it.

01:02:42.559 --> 01:02:44.150
People want to argue about it being a

01:02:44.160 --> 01:02:45.910
flat earth. It was not a flat earth;

01:02:45.920 --> 01:02:48.470
it's a ball. People go, "Well,

01:02:48.480 --> 01:02:49.990
Brandon, that doesn't line up."I'm telling

01:02:50.000 --> 01:02:52.630
you, it was a ball.

01:02:52.640 --> 01:02:56.870
It looked like a lump of clay.

01:02:56.880 --> 01:02:59.109
It was darkness; there was

01:02:59.119 --> 01:03:01.910
nothing. It was nothingness.

01:03:01.920 --> 01:03:04.230
As He spoke it, it all started to

01:03:04.240 --> 01:03:06.470
come about.

01:03:06.480 --> 01:03:08.630
I saw it. Then I saw Adam in

01:03:08.640 --> 01:03:11.990
the garden. He had a

01:03:12.000 --> 01:03:13.670
perfect beard; everything was

01:03:13.680 --> 01:03:16.789
perfect.

01:03:16.799 --> 01:03:18.470
I tried to tell people what Eve looked

01:03:18.480 --> 01:03:25.750
like. Eve had beautiful eyes.

01:03:25.760 --> 01:03:28.470
They were the most beautiful color of

01:03:28.480 --> 01:03:30.710
eyes; I've never seen eyes like them

01:03:30.720 --> 01:03:34.710
since.

01:03:34.720 --> 01:03:39.029
She was

01:03:39.029 --> 01:03:39.039
olive-skinned.

01:03:39.039 --> 01:03:41.589
She wasn't white,

01:03:41.599 --> 01:03:44.870
and she was not African-American dark.

01:03:44.880 --> 01:03:47.109
She was dark; she was like tan—very tan,

01:03:53.119 --> 01:03:55.029
darker than American Indian skin. Not

01:03:55.039 --> 01:04:02.230
that it matters, but people want to know.

01:04:02.240 --> 01:04:05.510
She looked oliveish. People ask, "What does

01:04:05.520 --> 01:04:08.390
that look like?"No, very dark like tan

01:04:08.400 --> 01:04:11.750
skin,

01:04:11.760 --> 01:04:13.990
but her hair was blacker than

01:04:14.000 --> 01:04:16.549
Diana's hair.

01:04:16.559 --> 01:04:18.950
Her eyes were the most

01:04:18.960 --> 01:04:22.390
beautiful color I've ever seen.

01:04:22.400 --> 01:04:23.829
In fact, I've tried to explain them to

01:04:23.839 --> 01:04:25.670
Diana. We've tried to find people's eyes

01:04:25.680 --> 01:04:29.190
that look like Eve's eyes. I said, "If I

01:04:29.200 --> 01:04:33.910
ever find them, Diana, I'll show

01:04:33.910 --> 01:04:33.920
you."They

01:04:33.920 --> 01:04:36.230
looked almost a

01:04:36.240 --> 01:04:40.069
greenish color

01:04:40.079 --> 01:04:43.029
with a mixture of brown

01:04:43.039 --> 01:04:45.990
and a little blue in them.

01:04:46.000 --> 01:04:49.990
Explain that—it was beautiful, the

01:04:50.000 --> 01:04:53.190
eye. I didn't see Adam's eyes, but Eve

01:04:53.200 --> 01:04:56.150
was sitting down

01:04:56.150 --> 01:04:56.160
with

01:04:56.160 --> 01:04:58.390
her hair around

01:04:58.400 --> 01:05:01.910
her. I saw her sitting on

01:05:01.910 --> 01:05:01.920
a

01:05:01.920 --> 01:05:05.349
little rock with

01:05:05.359 --> 01:05:09.029
ferns growing around her,

01:05:09.039 --> 01:05:11.510
and she was doing something, but it

01:05:11.520 --> 01:05:13.670
happened quickly.

01:05:13.680 --> 01:05:16.230
I was thinking, "What in the

01:05:16.240 --> 01:05:19.270
world?"Everything

01:05:19.280 --> 01:05:21.029
in the garden at that moment

01:05:21.039 --> 01:05:28.230
was glorious.

01:05:28.240 --> 01:05:34.150
It was beautiful

01:05:34.160 --> 01:05:35.750
going back and being able to see that

01:05:35.760 --> 01:05:37.510
again.

01:05:37.520 --> 01:05:40.549
Birds were the size of cars;

01:05:40.559 --> 01:05:43.430
they were truly massive. It was

01:05:43.440 --> 01:05:45.670
prehistoric. It was beautiful.

01:05:45.680 --> 01:05:48.630
Things weren't like now.

01:05:48.640 --> 01:05:50.069
Things were bigger: the trees were

01:05:50.079 --> 01:05:53.589
bigger, the plants were bigger. So, is

01:05:53.599 --> 01:05:55.589
that enough? I don't know

01:05:55.599 --> 01:05:57.430
if I answered that right. But I

01:05:57.440 --> 01:05:58.950
could see the pyramids; I could see

01:05:58.960 --> 01:06:00.470
everything being constructed. I

01:06:00.480 --> 01:06:01.990
think people think there

01:06:01.990 --> 01:06:02.000
are

01:06:02.000 --> 01:06:03.910
conspiracies happening, which is why

01:06:03.910 --> 01:06:03.920
they

01:06:03.920 --> 01:06:06.069
are

01:06:06.069 --> 01:06:06.079
asking

01:06:06.079 --> 01:06:07.029
about

01:06:07.029 --> 01:06:07.039
conspiracies—how

01:06:07.039 --> 01:06:09.430
it was built.

01:06:09.440 --> 01:06:11.510
I saw men building them. I

01:06:11.520 --> 01:06:13.589
didn't see aliens building the pyramids.

01:06:13.599 --> 01:06:15.349
They were men building the pyramids, and

01:06:18.319 --> 01:06:19.750
they had wooden things. They were

01:06:19.760 --> 01:06:21.670
dragging things around. People ask, "How'd that happen?"There were

01:06:23.440 --> 01:06:25.589
literally hundreds, if not thousands,

01:06:25.599 --> 01:06:27.510
of men moving these things around.

01:06:27.520 --> 01:06:30.069
I could see all these ramps and

01:06:30.079 --> 01:06:31.430
all this stuff being moved

01:06:31.440 --> 01:06:32.390
around.

01:06:34.000 --> 01:06:36.549
People say, "Well, how'd they lift

01:06:36.559 --> 01:06:38.549
a big stone like that?"They did.

01:06:38.559 --> 01:06:40.230
But there were bigger men. Now, if those

01:06:40.240 --> 01:06:42.710
were giants, I don't know, but

01:06:42.720 --> 01:06:45.190
it was happening quickly

01:06:45.200 --> 01:06:47.190
and panning out before my

01:06:47.200 --> 01:06:49.270
face.

01:06:49.280 --> 01:06:50.870
It was happening so

01:06:50.880 --> 01:06:52.950
fast that it was moving

01:06:52.960 --> 01:06:54.549
like this, and I was trying to glimpse it.

01:06:54.559 --> 01:06:57.510
I was looking at

01:06:57.510 --> 01:06:57.520
the

01:06:57.520 --> 01:07:01.109
Chinese Empire and all the

01:07:01.119 --> 01:07:03.589
things going on with the

01:07:03.599 --> 01:07:06.470
Great Wall of China;

01:07:06.480 --> 01:07:08.470
it was all being constructed

01:07:08.480 --> 01:07:10.150
right in front of my face. The Lord

01:07:10.160 --> 01:07:13.349
was just showing me things about time.

01:07:13.359 --> 01:07:17.270
And the city of Atlantis

01:07:17.280 --> 01:07:22.630
was out by Africa.

01:07:22.640 --> 01:07:25.510
It was an actual city. I saw it

01:07:25.520 --> 01:07:28.549
being swallowed up by fire and water.

01:07:28.559 --> 01:07:30.549
As it was

01:07:30.559 --> 01:07:32.230
playing out for me, I knew what

01:07:32.240 --> 01:07:33.910
it was. The Lord said to me, "This

01:07:33.920 --> 01:07:35.589
is the lost city of Atlantis."It

01:07:35.589 --> 01:07:35.599
was

01:07:35.599 --> 01:07:37.430
a

01:07:37.430 --> 01:07:37.440
mass—not

01:07:37.440 --> 01:07:39.510
just

01:07:39.520 --> 01:07:41.670
a little town. We're talking a

01:07:41.680 --> 01:07:44.309
massive thing, almost

01:07:44.319 --> 01:07:46.549
like an island,

01:07:46.559 --> 01:07:49.270
and it was destroyed.

01:07:49.280 --> 01:07:51.270
I could see the storm. I could see

01:07:51.280 --> 01:07:52.950
lightning. I could see things. There was

01:07:52.960 --> 01:07:56.309
something that happened.

01:07:56.319 --> 01:07:58.630
Brandon, that's way out there. A

01:07:58.640 --> 01:08:01.029
lot of things I don't share,

01:08:01.039 --> 01:08:02.950
because

01:08:02.950 --> 01:08:02.960
people—that's

01:08:02.960 --> 01:08:04.630
why I say if I can't usually back it up

01:08:04.640 --> 01:08:06.549
in scripture or whatever, I don't talk

01:08:06.559 --> 01:08:08.150
about a lot of things. But tonight I

01:08:08.160 --> 01:08:09.829
thought, well, I didn't have a lot. But

01:08:09.829 --> 01:08:09.839
I'll

01:08:09.839 --> 01:08:12.870
tell you some of the things I've seen

01:08:12.880 --> 01:08:15.190
and it's kind of interesting. I

01:08:15.200 --> 01:08:18.709
just keep a lot of things to myself.

01:08:18.709 --> 01:08:18.719
I

01:08:18.719 --> 01:08:20.550
just go, 'Well, you know, it's way out

01:08:20.560 --> 01:08:22.709
there. Are people going to believe

01:08:22.709 --> 01:08:22.719
it?'Well,

01:08:22.719 --> 01:08:24.309
there were dinosaurs, folks, and

01:08:24.319 --> 01:08:25.990
they were walking around Adam. It was a

01:08:26.000 --> 01:08:27.829
massive looking

01:08:27.829 --> 01:08:27.839
long-neck

01:08:27.839 --> 01:08:30.550
dinosaur, and he was talking to it, and

01:08:30.560 --> 01:08:33.430
it understood him

01:08:33.440 --> 01:08:36.470
as it was eating the trees. And Adam was

01:08:36.480 --> 01:08:38.870
talking to this thing. I don't know how

01:08:38.880 --> 01:08:40.789
it was like—did he speak dinosaur? I

01:08:40.799 --> 01:08:42.390
have no idea. But the dinosaur, like we

01:08:42.390 --> 01:08:42.400
talk

01:08:42.400 --> 01:08:44.229
to dogs and they listen to us,

01:08:44.239 --> 01:08:46.950
animals were listening to him. And

01:08:46.960 --> 01:08:49.269
that's why I was like, 'Look at

01:08:49.269 --> 01:08:49.279
that.'That

01:08:49.279 --> 01:08:51.829
big old long-neck dinosaur looks

01:08:51.839 --> 01:08:54.229
like one of those brachiosauruses that

01:08:54.239 --> 01:08:55.990
you know, like those long-neck dinosaurs

01:08:56.000 --> 01:09:03.349
on Jurassic Park. It was huge. It

01:09:03.349 --> 01:09:03.359
looked

01:09:03.359 --> 01:09:05.110
like a thunder lizard, a massive

01:09:05.120 --> 01:09:06.789
lizard,

01:09:06.799 --> 01:09:09.349
but

01:09:09.359 --> 01:09:11.189
I don't know. Father, we just

01:09:11.199 --> 01:09:13.669
thank you, Lord, for the body.

01:09:13.679 --> 01:09:15.030
Thank you, Lord, for all that you've

01:09:15.040 --> 01:09:18.870
done for us. Lord, you're so good to us.

01:09:18.880 --> 01:09:21.269
And Father, we don't take anything that

01:09:21.279 --> 01:09:24.550
you've done for granted. Nothing. And

01:09:24.560 --> 01:09:26.789
where we are in this dispensation of

01:09:26.799 --> 01:09:29.110
grace, where we are in this

01:09:29.110 --> 01:09:29.120
timeframe,

01:09:29.120 --> 01:09:32.550
Father, that you said Brandon, Diana,

01:09:32.560 --> 01:09:34.470
Brad, all of us come to this earth for

01:09:34.480 --> 01:09:37.510
such a time as this, that we were the

01:09:37.520 --> 01:09:40.309
closers. And you said, 'I've saved the

01:09:40.319 --> 01:09:42.470
best for last.

01:09:42.480 --> 01:09:48.149
All of you are saved the best for

01:09:48.149 --> 01:09:48.159
last.'You're

01:09:48.159 --> 01:09:50.229
my

01:09:50.239 --> 01:09:51.829
closers,

01:09:51.839 --> 01:09:54.390
every single one of us.

01:09:54.400 --> 01:09:56.550
I believe that this is the generation

01:09:56.560 --> 01:10:00.550
that will not taste death. And Father, I

01:10:00.560 --> 01:10:03.110
thank you for your body.

01:10:03.120 --> 01:10:05.350
This is what did it

01:10:05.360 --> 01:10:07.430
all.

01:10:07.440 --> 01:10:09.590
You paid the price for us to walk in

01:10:09.600 --> 01:10:12.070
victory. You paid the price for us to

01:10:12.080 --> 01:10:14.390
walk in healing. You paid the price for

01:10:14.400 --> 01:10:17.669
us to walk in deliverance. You paid the

01:10:17.679 --> 01:10:19.669
price for Diana and me, my children, and for

01:10:19.679 --> 01:10:21.510
all those that are watching. Father, for

01:10:21.520 --> 01:10:23.270
those that will continue to watch in

01:10:23.280 --> 01:10:25.110
the days, we pray for everyone in the

01:10:25.120 --> 01:10:27.510
world. You paid the price.

01:10:27.520 --> 01:10:29.750
Thank you, Lord.

01:10:29.760 --> 01:10:31.350
As we enter into this time of

01:10:31.360 --> 01:10:33.110
thanksgiving, as we enter into this

01:10:33.120 --> 01:10:34.790
time,

01:10:34.800 --> 01:10:38.630
we're so grateful.

01:10:38.640 --> 01:10:40.709
Thank you, Lord.

01:10:40.719 --> 01:10:42.870
We take this body right now in the name

01:10:42.880 --> 01:10:45.910
of Jesus. And we thank you, Lord,

01:10:45.920 --> 01:10:48.790
that we see that which is to come.

01:10:48.800 --> 01:10:50.310
Father, if there's anything you want us

01:10:50.320 --> 01:10:53.750
to see, let us have eyes to see and

01:10:53.760 --> 01:10:55.270
ears to hear what the spirit is

01:10:55.280 --> 01:10:57.750
saying. We take this body right now in

01:10:57.760 --> 01:11:00.070
Jesus'name.

01:11:00.080 --> 01:11:02.390
The anointing just hit my left

01:11:02.400 --> 01:11:03.669
hand. It's not the right hand. It's

01:11:03.679 --> 01:11:06.070
going to be this hand. I felt the

01:11:06.080 --> 01:11:07.590
Holy Ghost and fire hit all the way down

01:11:07.600 --> 01:11:10.470
to my elbow. That is very interesting.

01:11:10.480 --> 01:11:13.830
When I was holding the body,

01:11:13.840 --> 01:11:17.350
thank you Lord.

01:11:17.360 --> 01:11:19.750
Hallelujah. Diana,

01:11:19.760 --> 01:11:22.070
you believe for anything? I bless you in

01:11:22.070 --> 01:11:22.080
Jesus'name.

01:11:22.080 --> 01:11:24.310
Father, I thank you Lord for

01:11:24.320 --> 01:11:26.550
my wife healed and whole and well and

01:11:26.560 --> 01:11:28.390
filled with the power of God in

01:11:28.390 --> 01:11:28.400
Jesus'name.

01:11:28.400 --> 01:11:30.709
I feel if it's there, it's there

01:11:30.719 --> 01:11:32.790
for a reason. He doesn't just do

01:11:32.800 --> 01:11:35.750
that. Thank you Lord for the blood in

01:11:35.750 --> 01:11:35.760
Jesus'name.

01:11:35.760 --> 01:11:38.390
I'm actually feeling

01:11:38.400 --> 01:11:39.590
like I'm getting drunk in the Holy

01:11:39.600 --> 01:11:42.079
Ghost. That is amazing. Hallelujah.

01:11:50.239 --> 01:11:51.830
Wow.

01:12:43.040 --> 01:12:48.070
Hallelujah. Hallelujah.

01:12:48.080 --> 01:12:52.820
Wow. My tongue got it.

01:12:55.600 --> 01:13:00.025
Oh my goodness, Lord. Well, thank you,

01:13:00.035 --> 01:13:01.590
being filled with

01:13:01.600 --> 01:13:05.669
the Holy Ghost.

01:13:05.679 --> 01:13:08.070
Thank you, Lord, for the blood. Thank

01:13:08.080 --> 01:13:10.550
you,

01:13:10.560 --> 01:13:12.070
Father, that we make much of the blood

01:13:12.080 --> 01:13:14.630
and the blood makes much of us. Thank

01:13:14.640 --> 01:13:17.830
you for the blood. Hallelujah.

01:13:17.840 --> 01:13:19.350
Hallelujah.

01:13:19.360 --> 01:13:43.430
Glory to God. Thank you, Jesus.

01:13:43.440 --> 01:13:47.189
We take the blood today. We apply the

01:13:47.199 --> 01:13:52.550
blood

01:13:52.560 --> 01:13:55.750
over Diana,

01:13:55.760 --> 01:13:58.229
Braden,

01:13:58.239 --> 01:14:02.470
Megan Paisley, and me. I apply the blood.

01:14:02.480 --> 01:14:04.229
Where we make much of the blood, the

01:14:04.239 --> 01:14:08.149
blood makes much of us. We put angels

01:14:08.159 --> 01:14:10.550
all around and about us. Father, I thank

01:14:10.560 --> 01:14:12.550
you, Lord. Though we make much of the

01:14:12.560 --> 01:14:14.790
blood, we take the blood right now,

01:14:14.800 --> 01:14:16.070
Father. We thank you, Lord, that you

01:14:16.080 --> 01:14:18.550
forgive us of our sins

01:14:18.560 --> 01:14:35.830
in the name of Jesus. Amen and amen.

01:14:35.840 --> 01:14:37.350
You want a drink, baby?

01:14:37.360 --> 01:15:06.149
Thank you.

01:15:06.159 --> 01:15:09.590
Thank you, Lord.

01:15:09.600 --> 01:15:14.630
What can wash away my sin?

01:15:14.640 --> 01:15:20.310
Nothing but the blood of Jesus.

01:15:20.320 --> 01:15:25.590
Oh Father, fill our cup, Lord.

01:15:25.600 --> 01:15:28.709
We lift it up, Lord.

01:15:28.719 --> 01:15:31.510
Come and quench

01:15:31.520 --> 01:15:36.229
this thirsting of our soul.

01:15:36.239 --> 01:15:39.030
Bread of heaven,

01:15:39.040 --> 01:15:44.470
feed me till I want no more.

01:15:44.480 --> 01:15:49.030
Fill my cup, fill it up and make me

01:15:49.040 --> 01:15:52.149
whole.

01:15:52.159 --> 01:15:55.910
Fill our cup, Lord.

01:15:55.920 --> 01:16:00.229
I lift it up, Lord.

01:16:00.239 --> 01:16:04.390
Come and quench

01:16:04.400 --> 01:16:10.310
this thirsting of my soul.

01:16:10.320 --> 01:16:13.030
Bread of heaven,

01:16:13.040 --> 01:16:17.990
feed me till I want no more.

01:16:18.000 --> 01:16:22.470
Fill my cup. Fill it up and make me

01:16:22.480 --> 01:16:27.830
whole.

01:16:27.840 --> 01:16:31.669
Thank you, Lord.

01:16:31.679 --> 01:16:37.830
Fill our cup, Lord.

01:16:37.840 --> 01:16:46.870
I lift it up, Lord.

01:16:46.880 --> 01:16:52.950
Come and quench

01:16:52.960 --> 01:17:01.750
this thirsting of our soul.

01:17:01.760 --> 01:17:05.030
Bread of heaven,

01:17:05.040 --> 01:17:07.590
feed me till

01:17:07.600 --> 01:17:11.270
I want no more.

01:17:11.280 --> 01:17:13.910
Fill our cup.

01:17:13.920 --> 01:17:20.550
Fill it up and make me whole.

01:17:20.560 --> 01:17:23.270
I wish in the natural I could draw the

01:17:23.280 --> 01:17:27.268
pictures of what I saw,

01:17:27.278 --> 01:17:29.110
even about the pyramids and the

01:17:29.120 --> 01:17:31.110
things that I saw,

01:17:31.120 --> 01:17:34.550
the way the people looked

01:17:34.560 --> 01:17:40.229
as they were building things.

01:17:40.239 --> 01:17:41.990
The things that I have inside of me

01:17:42.000 --> 01:17:45.430
are such treasures.

01:17:45.440 --> 01:17:54.470
I could share them with everyone.

01:17:54.480 --> 01:17:58.950
How beautiful life is for all of us

01:17:58.960 --> 01:18:02.470
and we don't know it.

01:18:02.480 --> 01:18:05.669
Life is but a vapor and it moves so

01:18:05.679 --> 01:18:10.709
quickly.

01:18:10.719 --> 01:18:13.510
It's just a blink.

01:18:13.520 --> 01:18:17.189
What do we do with the blink we have?

01:18:17.199 --> 01:18:19.270
What do we do with the blink God's given

01:18:19.280 --> 01:18:23.669
us? It goes so quickly.

01:18:23.679 --> 01:18:25.590
What do we do with the relationship that

01:18:25.600 --> 01:18:29.910
he wants to have with every one of us?

01:18:29.920 --> 01:18:36.229
Life is a blink.

01:18:36.239 --> 01:18:39.990
