01:18:50.800 --> 01:19:10.470
Oh Father, I thank you Lord.

01:19:10.480 --> 01:19:12.070
Every one of us

01:19:12.080 --> 01:19:14.950
has

01:19:14.960 --> 01:19:16.630
something that

01:19:16.640 --> 01:19:20.630
God's called us to do.

01:19:20.640 --> 01:19:27.750
We do it with all our heart.

01:19:27.760 --> 01:19:29.350
Oh Lord, I thank you for your

01:19:29.360 --> 01:19:32.310
relationship.

01:19:32.320 --> 01:19:35.030
Oh Lord,

01:19:35.040 --> 01:19:40.229
you're beautiful.

01:19:40.239 --> 01:19:43.030
Your face

01:19:43.040 --> 01:19:45.350
is all

01:19:45.360 --> 01:19:46.550
I

01:19:46.560 --> 01:19:51.590
seek.

01:19:51.600 --> 01:19:54.070
And when

01:19:54.080 --> 01:19:56.550
your eyes

01:19:56.560 --> 01:19:58.870
are on

01:19:58.880 --> 01:20:00.470
this

01:20:00.480 --> 01:20:03.350
child,

01:20:03.360 --> 01:20:06.070
your grace

01:20:06.080 --> 01:20:08.310
abounds

01:20:08.320 --> 01:20:12.630
to me.

01:20:12.640 --> 01:20:15.590
Oh Lord,

01:20:15.600 --> 01:20:24.950
you're beautiful.

01:20:24.960 --> 01:20:28.390
Your face

01:20:28.400 --> 01:20:31.030
is all

01:20:31.040 --> 01:20:32.709
I

01:20:32.719 --> 01:20:35.910
see.

01:20:35.920 --> 01:20:38.950
Thank you, Father.

01:20:38.960 --> 01:20:41.030
There's so many of you that just

01:20:41.040 --> 01:20:44.870
