01:20:50.159 --> 01:20:53.669
He'll bring the rain on you. He'll bring

01:20:53.679 --> 01:20:57.030
the rain. It's like I had last night. I

01:20:57.030 --> 01:20:57.040
sat

01:20:57.040 --> 01:20:58.950
there and said, 'Lord, bring the

01:20:58.960 --> 01:21:02.229
