01:21:06.239 --> 01:21:07.990
I've poured out,

01:21:08.000 --> 01:21:09.830
Lord, and

01:21:09.840 --> 01:21:13.901
I need a fresh

01:21:13.901 --> 01:21:13.911
touch.'All

01:21:13.911 --> 01:21:20.709
you need is a drink.

01:21:20.719 --> 01:21:22.709
There's so many people here tonight that

01:21:22.719 --> 01:21:27.669
