01:21:30.560 --> 01:21:34.070
of false religion or just

01:21:34.080 --> 01:21:37.510
cookie-cutter.

01:21:37.520 --> 01:21:39.350
It's cookie-cutter. I don't say false

01:21:39.360 --> 01:21:42.070
religion, but just this

01:21:42.070 --> 01:21:42.080
Pharisaic

01:21:42.080 --> 01:21:44.790
religion. Jesus

01:21:44.800 --> 01:21:50.310
wants to become real to you.

01:21:50.320 --> 01:21:52.870
The Holy Spirit wants to become real to

01:21:52.880 --> 01:21:54.629
you.

01:21:54.639 --> 01:21:58.950
He's not a dove.

01:21:58.960 --> 01:22:01.830
He's not a

01:22:01.840 --> 01:22:08.229
feeling. He is a person.

01:22:08.239 --> 01:22:11.350
And he is more real to me

01:22:11.360 --> 01:22:13.830
