01:22:13.840 --> 01:22:16.310
I'm telling you, when he appeared and I

01:22:16.320 --> 01:22:17.910
was able to see him for the glimpse that

01:22:17.920 --> 01:22:20.390
I had, he's green. He's beautiful. He's

01:22:20.400 --> 01:22:25.910
alive.

01:22:25.920 --> 01:22:28.310
That probably just wrecked some people's

01:22:28.320 --> 01:22:32.229
world. But as I saw it, he's an

01:22:32.239 --> 01:22:37.750
