01:22:37.760 --> 01:22:43.189
It's like blue fire.

01:22:43.199 --> 01:22:45.510
An all-consuming fire that's blue but

01:22:45.520 --> 01:22:50.950
just has a green tint to it.

01:22:50.960 --> 01:22:55.990
The Holy Spirit

01:22:56.000 --> 01:22:57.669
has a form and he's

01:22:57.679 --> 01:23:06.229
barrel-chested. He's huge.

01:23:06.239 --> 01:23:09.030
I'm talking like

01:23:09.030 --> 01:23:09.040
a

01:23:09.040 --> 01:23:13.669
thick barrel-chested man.

01:23:13.679 --> 01:23:17.750
The Holy Spirit is not skinny. He's

01:23:17.760 --> 01:23:20.390
barrel-chested. He looks like he

01:23:20.400 --> 01:23:24.149
