01:23:41.280 --> 01:23:44.070
and I said, 'Oh,

01:23:44.080 --> 01:23:47.830
it's nothing what I thought.

01:23:47.840 --> 01:23:59.590
He's

01:23:59.590 --> 01:23:59.600
massive.'But

01:23:59.600 --> 01:24:01.430
he wants to become more so real to

01:24:01.440 --> 01:24:12.149
you.

01:24:12.159 --> 01:24:20.578
Oh Jesus.

01:24:24.400 --> 01:24:40.228
People

01:24:42.960 --> 01:24:46.550
want to know, 'Brandon, how do you

01:24:46.560 --> 01:24:49.430
have these

01:24:49.430 --> 01:24:49.440
experiences?'But

01:24:49.440 --> 01:24:51.430
every single one of them is so dear

01:24:51.440 --> 01:24:53.983
to me. I'll never forget any of them.

01:24:53.993 --> 01:24:55.430
It's like whenever you

01:24:55.440 --> 01:24:57.030
have something and you burn it on

01:24:58.560 --> 01:25:00.950
a piece of leather,

01:25:00.960 --> 01:25:03.910
it's ingrained there

01:25:03.910 --> 01:25:03.920
forever

01:25:03.920 --> 01:25:06.070
like cowhide.

01:25:06.080 --> 01:25:08.709
You brand it.

01:25:08.719 --> 01:25:11.350
Those experiences are branded in my

01:25:11.360 --> 01:25:14.870
mind. They're branded in me.

01:25:14.880 --> 01:25:18.390
They're always there. I can recall them.

01:25:18.400 --> 01:25:20.470
My mom said,

01:25:20.470 --> 01:25:20.480
"Brandon,

01:25:20.480 --> 01:25:22.790
you always have

01:25:22.800 --> 01:25:24.790
a memory like an

01:25:24.800 --> 01:25:26.070
elephant. You don't forget

01:25:26.070 --> 01:25:26.080
nothing."I

01:25:26.080 --> 01:25:31.319
know, but they truly are

01:25:31.319 --> 01:25:31.329
there,

01:25:31.329 --> 01:25:32.870
every single one of them,

01:25:32.880 --> 01:25:35.270
going to tribulation. I can recall them.

01:25:35.280 --> 01:25:41.430
They really happened.

01:25:41.440 --> 01:25:43.669
Every instance

01:25:43.679 --> 01:25:46.149
is so beautiful, and all the experiences

01:25:46.159 --> 01:25:49.030
that I've had with the Father.

01:25:49.040 --> 01:25:51.189
I can bring it back—from every angel

01:25:51.199 --> 01:25:53.990
encounter I've had to the

01:25:53.990 --> 01:25:54.000
demonic—I

01:25:54.000 --> 01:25:55.830
don't forget it. I remember it, and the

01:25:55.840 --> 01:26:00.139
