01:26:20.719 --> 01:26:22.470
When I've seen glimpses of

01:26:22.480 --> 01:26:24.950
heaven, I'm telling you all,

01:26:24.960 --> 01:26:31.270
you don't want to miss it.

01:26:31.280 --> 01:26:33.910
He's prepared a

01:26:33.920 --> 01:26:35.910
place for you that's so

01:26:35.920 --> 01:26:38.470
beautiful,

01:26:38.480 --> 01:26:43.510
and he wants you to go so bad.

01:26:43.520 --> 01:26:45.350
And to be absent from the body is to be

01:26:45.360 --> 01:26:47.270
present with the Lord. You know,

01:26:47.280 --> 01:26:48.790
whenever you almost died giving

01:26:48.800 --> 01:26:54.709
birth to Paisley,

01:26:54.719 --> 01:26:57.350
Diana said

01:26:57.360 --> 01:26:59.750
when she was stepping over and

01:26:59.760 --> 01:27:01.669
the doctor almost lost her after her

01:27:01.679 --> 01:27:04.229
C-section,

01:27:04.239 --> 01:27:07.270
her blood pressure dropped so bad. She

01:27:07.280 --> 01:27:08.950
said,

01:27:08.960 --> 01:27:11.270
"You tell them what you

01:27:11.280 --> 01:27:16.149
felt."Whenever

01:27:16.159 --> 01:27:17.990
it

01:27:18.000 --> 01:27:19.669
was,

01:27:19.679 --> 01:27:22.870
it was as easy as—it was easier than

01:27:22.880 --> 01:27:25.270
anything I've ever experienced in my

01:27:25.280 --> 01:27:27.430
life. It was just like breathing and I

01:27:27.440 --> 01:27:31.910
felt such a peace, just

01:27:31.920 --> 01:27:33.669
more peace than I've ever

01:27:33.679 --> 01:27:35.910
had in my whole life.

01:27:35.920 --> 01:27:38.229
And it was like breathing, like I

01:27:38.239 --> 01:27:40.470
was there. It

01:27:40.480 --> 01:27:42.310
would have been easier to go than it

01:27:42.320 --> 01:27:45.030
would have been to stay.

01:27:45.040 --> 01:27:47.830
And I really, really wanted to go because

01:27:47.840 --> 01:27:50.149
this peace was

01:27:50.159 --> 01:27:51.750
indescribable,

01:27:56.000 --> 01:27:59.750
peace on another level

01:27:59.760 --> 01:28:04.790
that a human can't understand,

01:28:06.639 --> 01:28:08.550
because the Holy Spirit brings so much

01:28:08.560 --> 01:28:12.229
peace to us here in this body, in

01:28:12.239 --> 01:28:15.110
our earthly vessels. But whenever I was

01:28:15.120 --> 01:28:20.470
in that moment,

01:28:20.480 --> 01:28:25.430
I can't describe it.

01:28:27.360 --> 01:28:29.990
I have no vocabulary to describe

01:28:30.000 --> 01:28:35.376
it, but it was beautiful and it

01:28:36.560 --> 01:28:39.510
felt like the way we're supposed to

01:28:39.520 --> 01:28:41.990
be, like the way we're supposed to feel.

01:28:42.000 --> 01:28:44.390
That peace just makes you feel

01:28:44.400 --> 01:28:46.709
alive, like this is life. It

01:28:46.719 --> 01:28:48.310
didn't feel like dying; it felt like

01:28:48.320 --> 01:28:51.189
living.

01:28:51.199 --> 01:28:53.990
I don't know how else to describe it. It

01:28:54.000 --> 01:28:57.030
was beautiful. I'll never forget it.

01:29:00.880 --> 01:29:03.189
I have no vocabulary; that's the closest

01:29:03.199 --> 01:29:06.390
thing I can get to describing it.

01:29:06.400 --> 01:29:07.830
I remember seeing your eyes

01:29:07.830 --> 01:29:07.840
and

01:29:07.840 --> 01:29:10.229
I told her, "You're

01:29:10.239 --> 01:29:12.470
going to lose her. She's going."And I

01:29:12.480 --> 01:29:13.750
could see it. I could feel it. And I

01:29:13.760 --> 01:29:15.270
grabbed a hold of your foot and I

01:29:15.280 --> 01:29:16.470
was praying, "No,

01:29:16.480 --> 01:29:18.870
you ain't dying on me.

01:29:18.880 --> 01:29:23.669
You ain't dying on me."They

01:29:23.669 --> 01:29:23.679
rushed

01:29:23.679 --> 01:29:25.910
in there and she

01:29:25.910 --> 01:29:25.920
coded,

01:29:25.920 --> 01:29:27.910
and they brought all their nurses in

01:29:27.920 --> 01:29:30.149
there to help her.

01:29:30.159 --> 01:29:31.830
I remember thinking, "She's slipping

01:29:31.840 --> 01:29:36.149
over right now. She's leaving

01:29:36.149 --> 01:29:36.159
me,"and

01:29:36.159 --> 01:29:40.950
they brought her back.

01:29:40.960 --> 01:29:44.709
You know, that

01:29:44.709 --> 01:29:44.719
in-between,

01:29:44.719 --> 01:29:46.709
that

01:29:46.719 --> 01:29:48.310
place where you're about ready to go

01:29:48.310 --> 01:29:48.320
home—in

01:29:48.320 --> 01:29:49.910
that instance

01:29:49.920 --> 01:29:51.910
where Diana was in birth like that

01:29:51.920 --> 01:29:54.470
and she lost

01:29:54.480 --> 01:29:56.149
so much blood,

01:29:56.149 --> 01:29:56.159
it

01:29:56.159 --> 01:29:57.669
was really

01:29:57.679 --> 01:29:59.910
scary in the natural for me, but

01:29:59.920 --> 01:30:02.070
I could see the peace on her face. And

01:30:02.070 --> 01:30:02.080
she

01:30:02.080 --> 01:30:05.189
said, "Pray for

01:30:05.189 --> 01:30:05.199
me."And

01:30:05.199 --> 01:30:06.629
all of a sudden, that was the

01:30:06.639 --> 01:30:08.709
last thing she said for a second, and she

01:30:08.719 --> 01:30:10.550
went poof and her eyes got dark. I

01:30:10.560 --> 01:30:12.870
went, "What's going on? Is she

01:30:12.880 --> 01:30:18.229
truly about to

01:30:18.229 --> 01:30:18.239
die?"But

01:30:18.239 --> 01:30:21.030
they brought her back,

01:30:21.040 --> 01:30:22.870
all to the glory of God. Thank you,

01:30:22.880 --> 01:30:29.030
Jesus.

01:30:29.040 --> 01:30:32.310
I just try to

01:30:32.320 --> 01:30:35.110
bring the Lord

01:30:35.120 --> 01:30:36.629
in these things. When

01:30:36.639 --> 01:30:38.149
he visits and he's talking, I feel

01:30:38.159 --> 01:30:41.750
his presence so strong right now.

01:30:41.760 --> 01:30:43.830
I want you to realize that he wants a

01:30:43.840 --> 01:30:45.750
relationship more with you than what you

01:30:45.760 --> 01:30:50.870
want one with him.

01:30:50.880 --> 01:30:53.510
It's more real, y'all,

01:30:53.520 --> 01:30:56.470
