01:31:12.588 --> 01:31:13.990
But he is a respecter of faith

01:31:14.000 --> 01:31:17.750
and he is a respecter of relationship and time.

01:31:17.760 --> 01:31:21.030
When you die to yourself in time sitting

01:31:21.040 --> 01:31:26.870
before him, when you lose yourself,

01:31:26.880 --> 01:31:29.669
there is a level

01:31:29.679 --> 01:31:32.950
