01:31:32.960 --> 01:31:35.990
desperate, how hungry, how thirsty are

01:31:36.000 --> 01:31:37.910
you?

01:31:37.920 --> 01:31:42.709
Is he your every breath?

01:31:42.719 --> 01:31:44.629
Is he as much as you want your next

01:31:44.639 --> 01:31:47.350
drink of water?

01:31:47.360 --> 01:31:48.790
I'm going to tell you, some days it's not

01:31:48.800 --> 01:31:51.910
like that for me because the

01:31:51.920 --> 01:31:53.990
world distracts you. This channel, I'm

01:31:54.000 --> 01:31:55.270
going to tell you, is more distraction

01:31:55.280 --> 01:31:57.750
than it's ever been in my life. Sharing

01:31:57.760 --> 01:32:00.470
myself with this—if I didn't have

01:32:00.480 --> 01:32:02.390
this, I know where I'd already be: at my

01:32:02.400 --> 01:32:05.510
laundry room machine, sitting by

01:32:05.520 --> 01:32:09.110
my dryer praying, or in my closet, or

01:32:09.120 --> 01:32:11.189
sitting on the porch talking,

01:32:11.199 --> 01:32:13.669
