01:32:15.280 --> 01:32:16.870
I miss those times. It's like I said to

01:32:16.880 --> 01:32:19.590
him last night, "Lord, I'm so

01:32:19.600 --> 01:32:21.669
tired. I'm so thirsty. I've dumped out

01:32:21.679 --> 01:32:24.709
all week and I just need you to help

01:32:24.719 --> 01:32:26.470
me."I

01:32:26.480 --> 01:32:28.950
said, "Are you mad at me? Is our

01:32:28.960 --> 01:32:31.270
relationship cooled off out of

01:32:31.270 --> 01:32:31.280
insecurity?"I

01:32:31.280 --> 01:32:34.390
said, "Lord, are we cool?

01:32:34.400 --> 01:32:35.990
Are we alright?"He said,

01:32:36.000 --> 01:32:37.910
"Brandon, you're tired. I'm not mad at

01:32:37.910 --> 01:32:37.920
you.

01:32:37.920 --> 01:32:39.590
Why would I be mad at you?

01:32:39.600 --> 01:32:44.950
You've helped me, Brandon.

01:32:44.960 --> 01:32:51.590
I want to help

01:32:51.600 --> 01:32:54.229
you."But

01:32:54.239 --> 01:32:55.910
I don't want to lose myself in all

01:32:55.920 --> 01:32:58.709
this.

01:32:58.719 --> 01:33:00.470
You can gain the whole world and lose

01:33:00.480 --> 01:33:03.030
your soul. I don't want to lose my

01:33:03.040 --> 01:33:04.470
relationship with you because of the

01:33:04.480 --> 01:33:11.510
people

01:33:11.520 --> 01:33:13.830
pulling all the time.

01:33:13.840 --> 01:33:16.070
But I understood why the

01:33:16.080 --> 01:33:17.990
disciples took their time and

01:33:18.000 --> 01:33:20.310
they gave it away, but at the same time

01:33:20.320 --> 01:33:21.990
it's so desperate because there's so

01:33:22.000 --> 01:33:24.629
many people with so many needs.

01:33:24.639 --> 01:33:26.950
There's so many people that are going to

01:33:26.960 --> 01:33:29.030
hell. There's so many people that

01:33:29.040 --> 01:33:31.669
just don't know. And I thought,

01:33:31.679 --> 01:33:34.070
if I pour myself out and you can pull

01:33:34.080 --> 01:33:36.310
them out of that pit,

01:33:36.320 --> 01:33:37.830
if I could help

01:33:37.840 --> 01:33:40.790
just the 58 of you tonight, I

01:33:40.800 --> 01:33:42.070
felt like I accomplished something

01:33:42.080 --> 01:33:44.709
today. But there's

01:33:44.719 --> 01:33:46.870
something to have an authentic relationship

01:33:46.880 --> 01:33:50.070
with God

01:33:50.080 --> 01:33:54.470
when you just sit and talk to him.

01:33:54.480 --> 01:33:56.390
And you don't worry about anybody else

01:33:56.400 --> 01:33:58.470
and what their opinion is because all of

01:33:58.480 --> 01:34:01.750
it changes like the tide.

01:34:01.760 --> 01:34:03.910
Who cares?

01:34:03.920 --> 01:34:06.550
But there is an authentic move; there's

01:34:06.560 --> 01:34:08.774
an authentic presence

01:34:08.784 --> 01:34:15.325
that is tangible.

01:34:15.335 --> 01:34:21.189
And

01:34:21.199 --> 01:34:22.950
every prayer time is so

01:34:22.960 --> 01:34:26.310
